Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀疑近卫史菜就是顶之座  赫卡特的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在来袭的徒面前作了一个极限赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于面临着危机也一动不动的史菜  夏娜终于打消了疑虑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  看着接近着悠二的史菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜的心中再次出现了新的动荡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫同学  最近一段时间我每天早上都会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什么烦恼的话  请尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫  你又出麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来需要一个人时刻照看着你才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是最为合适的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫  你坐到池的旁边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  还不快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得是悠二不可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她好像有点粘着我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她习惯这里的生活前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得在各方面都好好帮助她才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  坂井君  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  近卫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是专程在这里等我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为明明我也是要照看近卫同学的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却把接送近卫同学的工作都交给坂井君你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说过了不用在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为吉田同学你家刚好是相反的方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上学放学就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在女孩子的一些问题方面就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点走上课会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么体育课会叫我们打扫游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  总比对着书桌好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫同学  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在偷什么懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  这样拿着刷子  感觉像往前推
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回敬你  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢来就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊  我在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天吃的也是干鲣鱼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那么喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  干鲣鱼的饭团很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井你可真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然可以吃两个便当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  近卫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是一美为了坂井君才做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必在意  没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就一点点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  这个你也想…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我已经给悠二你了  随你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  吉田同学  明天再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样目送着他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也跟过去如何呢  本来你就负责照看她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照看她…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连吉田一美也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时只有我跟悠二两个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那家店是新开的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊  明天开张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有趣呢  明天放学的时候  也叫上池大家一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大碗天国…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  近卫史菜不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫同学  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可都是为了陪你才这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这方面你注意一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着那么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要到这种地方来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说  到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个转校生也没有任何的异常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  她大概是我们学校里最不会惹是生非的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外界宿那边应该已经作出回应了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还没有任何假面舞会重新开始活动了的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是无中生有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把赫卡特单独一人送往火雾战士身边这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是贝鲁佩尔也不可能会做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  既然零时迷子带着戒禁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能明白你想要慎重的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  「外界宿」到底指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们火雾战士进行情报交换的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互助设施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是讨厌被淋湿的火雾战士们会聚集的极少数的地方之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方那么悠闲地待着真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小丫头与密斯提斯的小弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在估计锻炼正进展得火热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔几次没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你已经有点认同悠二了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天  那里以及这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就都当作是欢乐时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井那家伙  竟以火雾战士为对手在进行着训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏  夏娜  是不是比以前更猛烈了点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…  我会如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井悠二  要从力量的脉动去感知动作的始动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的感知能力非常敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内还蕴藏着能够匹敌红世之王的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据你日后的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还能发现一条与普通的火炬  普通的密斯提斯都不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的道路？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  只有你才能够前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二一定能够变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要努力的话一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你不被无关紧要的事所迷惑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大碗天国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这家店了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是少见啊  佐藤和田中居然也来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到大碗以后哪还坐得住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大碗咖喱久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大碗猪排饭久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大碗拉面久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大碗又一丁拉面久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够资格做我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井  决一胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不大明白  但我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  真打算一个人吃完它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们才是  三个人吃的话不就没意义了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说已经算很多的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个  都不要太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上  都给我放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在干什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  平手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  近卫同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫同学不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还以为会在洗手间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么悠二必须去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于为什么  毕竟我是照顾她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在是回家的路上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也约好送她回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前已经警告过近卫史菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不作声就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有必要去找她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的家伙  别管就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做到那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都知道她不是徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这事无关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我没看好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也分头去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是从野猫那里救下来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是把胡萝卜洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我是在嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的心情  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天晚上开始  我将成为你的陪练
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们好像很喜欢那个新窝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜同学不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上的锻炼也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学到图书委员会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因史菜的事情而感情无法平静的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因夏娜的言行而困惑的威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因一点小争执引起了夏娜的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可奈何的威尔艾米娜  得到了悠二的母亲千草的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  灼眼的夏娜第二季
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭的餐桌
